==English==
==={{initialism}}===
'''WTF''' ''or'' '''wtf'''

#(''taboo Internet slang'') [[What the fuck]].
# World Taekwondo Federation

====Usage note====
'''WTF''' may be used to introduce a question, as in "WTF are you talking about?" or as an interjection "WTF?  That's a load of bull!" Sometimes substituted with "whiskey tango foxtrot."

